<h3><a href="#ipTalkCommunity">APIC&rsquo;s IP Talk community</a></h3>
<div style="text-align: left;">
<p>Log on to <a href="http://community.apic.org/myapic/communities/viewcommunities/groupdetails?CommunityKey=a42080cc-43bc-4706-beba-216aa38f9940" target="_blank">IP Talk</a>, APIC&rsquo;s peer-to-peer online community, to engage in conversations about Ebola with other infection preventionists. Type &ldquo;Ebola&rdquo; in the search bar to review conversations and resources posted by other infection preventionists.</p>
